　　華　　民　　國　　111 　年　　2 　　月　　25　　日\r\n                                      書記官  蔡秀貞","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/TCDV/103%2c%e9%87%8d%e8%a8%b4%2c631%2c20220225%2c2/pdf"},"JID":"TCDV,103,重訴,631,20220225,2","JYEAR":"103","JCASE":"重訴","JNO":"631","JDATE":"20220225","JTITLE":"損害賠償"}